Story
The boy who cried Wolf!!!

 
Once there was a boy named Freddy he was a shepard. One day he was very bored.
To gain some attention from the villagers and to have some fun he got an idea; A very ridiculous 
idea. He looked here and there and took a deep breathe and looked at the hills beside a village 
one person was on his way towards the village with his horse. "Wolf!" the boy cried hoping he 
would get his attention suddenly the horse galloped towards young Freddy as the horse towered over him
the Villager got off to help him he asked where was the wolf the boy aswered "there was no wolf".
The Village was angery as he galloped away on his horse he said "next time i will not help you".
